com.navis.framework.portal.query

Class ValueHolderFilterAndSort

  • java.lang.Object
    • com.navis.framework.portal.query.ValueHolderFilterAndSort

  • public final class ValueHolderFilterAndSort
extends java.lang.Object
    Combines filter and sort operations Notes: 1. Null compares as greater than not-null 2. Each step operates on a mutable collection, which is returned to the caller at the end. The sort step may fail on an incomparable field without an effect on the result.
    Author:
    mozessi, 1/27/2016
